title: Don't Miss This 2 Bed 1 Bath at Bellwether
posting_body: ['Welcome to Bellwether Apartment Homes where we feature lovely, one, two, and three bedroom apartment homes.', 'Bellwether is adjacent to I5, a variety of restaurants, shopping, the Chehalis Trail, colleges and so much more!', '**Must be flexible with move-in time frame!', 'Date listed is only estimated and not guaranteed.', '**', 'Featured Apartment Home:', '☑4-102 / 1st Floor/ Sub-level', '☑Newly renovated 2 bedroom / 1 bath / 900 square feet', '☑$1,755/Month* Resident pays all utilities.', '☑Indoor hot tub', '☑2 seasonal outdoor pools', '☑Fitness center', '☑Outdoor basketball court', '☑Gated dog park', '☑Unlimited tanning', '☑On-site, licensed childcare and preschool', '☑Full Size Washer/Dryer in unit', '☑2 Vehicle Max Per Apartment/1 covered parking space is included', '☑ 6 - 12 Month Lease', '☑100% Non-Smoking (includes vaping) anywhere on the property', '☑Pet-friendly/45lb weight restriction for dogs', '☑Pet Rent: $25/monthly (per pet)', 'Bellwether Apartment Homes', '1400 Fones Rd.', 'SE', 'Olympia, WA 98501', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Website: <URL>']
